import React from 'react'
import './assets/css/base/base.css'
import { BrowserRouter, Route, Switch } from 'react-router-dom'

import Home from './paginas/Home'
import Sobre from './paginas/Sobre'

function App() {
  
  return (
    <>
      <BrowserRouter>
        <Switch>

        </Switch>

        <Route exact path='/'>
          <Home/>
        </Route>
        <Route path='/sobre'>
          <Sobre/>
        </Route>
      </BrowserRouter>

    </>
  )
}

export default App
